First thing you do is add a little bit of salt

00:07:43.540 --> 00:07:46.400
Drain off our peas

00:07:47.100 --> 00:07:49.220
Wedge of lemon, 

00:07:49.220 --> 00:07:51.020
our cod,

00:07:54.270 --> 00:07:57.630
beautiful crispy chips,

00:07:57.630 --> 00:08:00.600
our peas,

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:03.990
then lovely thick tartar sauce

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:08.900
and there you have it, that's my 

